ee - 5+ Years' Communications and/or Public Relations experience - Influencer Marketing/Brand Ambassador Management - Crypto enthusiast and trader that deeply understands the motives of crypto users and traders - Familiar with the emerging DeFi landscape and what differentiates projects from one another - Strong English writing and communication - Active social media user on platforms where crypto users live (Telegram, Twitter, Wechat, Reddit, etc) BONUS - Fluency in Chinese, Korean, Russian, Vietnamese or Spanish What's In It for You - Competitive Salary - Fast-paced start-up environment - Stock Options and company tokens - Gym membership - Flex vacation policy - 100% paid medical, dental and vision - 401K with match So, if you are a Communications/PR Manager who is passionate about crypto and blockchain tech, apply today! Security Clearance will be needed - therefore, only US citizens can be considered. ", 
